  <part id="loom-base">
    <title>Loom Reference</title>

    <partintro>

    <para>
      Loom is yet another network manager for GNU/Linux with a easy to use 
      <ulink type="http" url="http:///dbus.freedesktop.org">DBus</ulink>
      Interface.
      User <emphasis>root</emphasis> and users of group
      <emphasis>netdev</emphasis> are allowed to introspect, send and receive
      methods, emit and watch signals.
    </para>

    </partintro>

